 />\n<br />\n打仗時候食嘅嘢. 班垃圾竟然畀幾百蚊去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要打卡. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6qbcuda0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6qbcuda0&h=780f77e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f21e6dcd64b058c600bca81ca31cd0cbf1c5b3f","tid":398860,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梳乎厘pancake</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係成日喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇食過.好唔好食?"},{"pid":"396e214cb80371bc1cb8b3c44f696a19f5caf620","tid":398860,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"仲有抹荼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 濫撚曬"},{"pid":"6563770ed60dcc7c3d2a86a99b8e81e925d192cf","tid":398860,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"兩個垃圾港女偷偷腐皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4416466a35d0b1ebe23fd744b5c98e76dbde2a","tid":398860,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"屎"}]}